text: Carlos Romero (born 6 July 1942) is a Mexican wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 78 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Mexico Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Campeche
